title: Gecko's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. The staff speaks English. A good place to begin a night out or end a long day at the beach. Directions: facing the ocean turn left and walk to near end of beach, it's on the first floor at the far end of Pale De CZ building which also houses the vegan-friendly Smoothie King. Vegans please confirm if options are offered and inform HappyCow.
